  <front>
   <head>Epigrammi - XLVII. Ad Rufum.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Tamquam prisca mihi, saxoque inventa vetusto,</l>
     <l n="2">Disticha, Rufe, soles saepe referre tua.</l>
     <l n="3">Stultum adeo me, Rufe, putas? ego tam mala credam</l>
     <l n="4">Carmina Romano marmore posse legi?</l>
     <l n="5">Archemoro longos affingis Nestoris annos.</l>
     <l n="6">Andromaches puerum Laomedonta vocas.</l>
     <l n="7">Desine mentiri Pyliam, Phrygiamque senectam.</l>
     <l n="8">Sint vetera haec aliis, mi nova semper erunt.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
